{"t": "2026-04-27T00:26:54.007538+00:00", "iter": 39, "type": "tool", "name": "bash", "args": {"command": "cd /workspace && git add logalyzer/output.py && git commit -m 'Replace hand-rolled JSON with json.dumps in output module\n\nThe original to_json() built JSON strings by hand using f-strings,\nwhich is fragile: special characters in URLs (e.g. quotes, backslashes)\nwould produce invalid JSON. The render_aggregate JSON path had the same\nissue.\n\nSwitch to json.dumps which handles escaping correctly. This also\nproduces properly formatted JSON output that can be parsed by any\nJSON consumer.'"}, "wall_s": 0.06, "result_len": 162}
